{"tid":1957853,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲紅唔起系列 - 有冇巴絲係Hi-Rez studios 粉絲?","createTime":"2020-04-04T07:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T13:18:57.000Z","uid":214732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"448e8ff29160bba4f36da7488e3ccca53835a804","tid":1957853,"uid":214732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"Hi Rez studios 3大巨頭遊戲<br />\nSmite<br />\nPaladins<br />\nRealm Royale<br />\n<br />\n同埋黎緊會出隻Rogue Company<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有玩開呢幾隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為每次呢3隻game各自出既post<br />\n傾3頁左右就收皮，實在太少人玩<br />\n所以今次試下水溫group埋一齊傾下<br />\n睇下反應係點<br />\n<br />\n利伸<br />\n我就主玩smite,由s1玩到依家<br />\n由pc轉去ps4<br />\n<br />\npaladins都有玩，但玩極都好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRR就因為搵唔到fd玩，暫時未正式入坑"},{"pid":"98bcd156865c2215bbbaf98e62760fdd0513f506","tid":1957853,"uid":321313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3119cf355a7dd1aa7fa5e1ebc531e3ef841be738","tid":1957853,"uid":214732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20853c857fdb221d70123138811bffd34a7ecd58","tid":1957853,"uid":214732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a9f44c969297178cf244aaff309568d0e2cd8e","tid":1957853,"uid":214732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T10:57:37.000Z","msg":"真係無人玩到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e62169f93c37aa8c39a250c2f67a71bc3c230d1","tid":1957853,"